race.description: Carlin & Gazzard Open Stake Pr1 Division1
race.comment: CADILLAC RAGTOP (7) turned in a modest effort most recently when fifth at Horsham over 410m behind Paw Imperial (23.97) in a Grade 4/5. Was a winner the start prior. Can bounce back. ROCKLEA EARLE (1) finished in the placings last time but could not have been more impressive before that in his speedy 17.67 win at this track over 305m. Top win two back and rates a key player again. MISTER CADILLAC (3) last start finished 4th on September 30 over 410m at Horsham behind Paw Imperial beaten 7 lengths (23.96) in a Grade 4/5. Looks a key player on best form. RIVIA UMIKO (2) did a good job to finish second last time out over 400m at Geelong (23.04) in a Grade 5, the second top-three finish on the trot.
